title: Wenger Men's 01.1043.102"Urban Classic" Silver-Tone Chrono Watch with Mesh Bracelet
feature: Round silver-tone chronograph watch featuring date window at four o’clock position with three subdials on black stamped dial
Features fold-over clasp closure on mesh bracelet
Water-resistant to 100 m (330 ft): suitable for snorkeling, as well as swimming, but not diving
description: Wenger 01.1043.102 Urban Classic chronograph men's watch features a 43mm wide and 12mm thick solid stainless steel case with crystals accented fixed bezel and textured push-pull crown with functions pushers. Wenger 01.1043.102 is powered by a reliable Swiss Ronda Z60 quartz chronograph movement. This stylish watch also features a textured black dial with white accents silver tone luminous hands and hour markers along with the chronograph and day-date display functions, scratch resistant sapphire coated mineral crystal and water resistant to 100 meters. Wenger 01.1043.102 is equipped with a 23mm wide solid stainless steel mesh bracelet with a fold over clasp. Wenger 01.1043.102 men's Urban Classic chronograph black dial steel mesh bracelet watch is brand new and comes in an original Wenger gift box and is backed by a 3 years limited warranty.
